<http://www.example.org/emdco#isReusable> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isReusable> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.example.org/emdco#MedicalDevice> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isReusable> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isReusable> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Indicates whether the device can be used more than once." .
<http://www.example.org/emdco#isReusable> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is reusable" .
